race.description: Tabtouch Download The App Today Maiden
race.comment: WAHOOCHINO (7) stuck on well over 1400m at Bunbury last time out when the race favourite and now jumps right out in trip. The form out of his last start has already been franked and this trip looks perfect for him now third-up. Draw is sticky, but he looks to have stacks up upside. VAMPI QUEEN (15) was solid from up on the pace last start at Ascot, beaten 3L over the mile as the race favourite. Drawn right out here, but Parnham can roll forward if he wishes down the long back straight. Can improve again out in trip. MY TEA (1) closed nicely to be 1.3L off the winner at Bunbury last time out over 1705m. The rise in trip and better gate are both big ticks for him. Can raise the bar again here. BONDI EXPRESS (3) hasn't been far away in recent efforts and has already ticked the distance box. Can feature. HEAVENLY RAPTURE (16) can sit much closer today and a win isn't out of the question.
